Ingress
Question 13
Create a new ingress resource named echo in echo-sound namespace.
With the following tasks:
Espose the deployment with a service named echo-service on http://example.org/echo using Service port 8080 type=NodePort.
The availability of Service echo-service can be checked using the following command which should return 200:
curl -o /dev/null -s -w “%{http_code}\n” http://example.org/echo
환경설정
kubectl create ns echo-sound
kubectl create deploy echoserver-deployment -n echo-sound --image=tomcat
